methods.name: snitchCheck
methods.desc: Used to check the behavior of a Validator App

args.name: params
args.desc: SnitchInfo object containing the informations to check

returns.desc: boolean result of the snitch if successfull - true

methods.name: reStakeFromSnitch
methods.desc: Follow up operation called by the snitched App to perform restaking of the delegated Algo clawed back

args.name: snitchedApp
args.desc: The AppID of the validator to snitch

args.name: receiverApp
args.desc: The AppID of the receiver of the delegated Algo

args.name: restakeTxn
args.desc: The PayTxn following the snitch that sends the delegated Algo to be moved back and restaked

methods.name: onOperatorExit
methods.desc: Used to close and delete a validator pool contract, only callable by the node operator.

args.name: appToClose
args.desc: The AppID of the operator to close
